43
00:05:14,523 --> 00:05:17,901
NOT PRIVY TO CEO'S PRIVATE LIFE,
A CAUSE FOR CELEBRATION IF TRUE

44
00:05:17,984 --> 00:05:19,319
Your Majesty.

45
00:05:19,402 --> 00:05:20,987
