and the possibility of marriage.

59
00:06:14,708 --> 00:06:16,459
Are you throwing a tantrum?

60
00:06:18,169 --> 00:06:19,588
Premarital pregnancy…

61
00:06:23,884 --> 00:06:25,176
You can rest assured

62
00:06:25,802 --> 00:06:27,512
