69
00:07:02,088 --> 00:07:03,298
Seong Huiju.

70
00:07:03,381 --> 00:07:04,758
Oh. You're here.

71
00:07:04,841 --> 00:07:06,259
Uncle.

72
00:07:08,511 --> 00:07:10,138
See, I told you it'd be spicy.

73
00:07:10,221 --> 00:07:11,765
Have some water.

74
00:07:11,848 --> 00:07:12,891
I am fine.

75
00:07:21,691 --> 00:07:24,986
Your Majesty,
what are you doing here at this late hour?

76
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:27,739
He said he was having trouble sleeping--

77
00:07:27,822 --> 00:07:28,948
I did not ask you.

78
00:07:30,325 --> 00:07:32,452
I was having trouble sleeping.

79
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:40,418
So I came by.

80
00:07:40,919 --> 00:07:42,420
What does having trouble sleeping

81
00:07:44,130 --> 00:07:45,423
have to do with this?

82
00:07:46,424 --> 00:07:50,095
She said a full belly
would help me fall asleep.

83
00:08:01,106 --> 00:08:02,399
Come in, Court Lady Jung.

84
00:08:11,199 --> 00:08:12,200
Your Majesty.

85
00:08:13,910 --> 00:08:15,912
Shall I escort you
to Queen Mother's quarters?

86
00:08:25,839 --> 00:08:28,007
You couldn't just let him
finish it in peace?

87
00:08:32,387 --> 00:08:34,055
I mean, come on.

88
00:08:34,597 --> 00:08:37,308
A bowl of ramyeon
wouldn't have taken that long to finish.

89
00:08:41,187 --> 00:08:42,689
And if he suffers indigestion?

90
00:08:43,523 --> 00:08:44,858
You would be wholly to blame.

91
00:08:45,692 --> 00:08:47,610
And if Queen Mother is angered?

92
00:08:48,194 --> 00:08:50,238
All that over a measly bowl of ramyeon?

93
00:08:50,321 --> 00:08:51,364
The Queen Mother…

94
00:08:53,658 --> 00:08:54,659
denied the request.

95
00:09:02,625 --> 00:09:03,626
Well…

96
00:09:04,127 --> 00:09:05,628
we expected as much.

97
00:09:06,212 --> 00:09:08,465
But you know, it still doesn't feel great.

98
00:09:08,548 --> 00:09:10,175
Like I'm being bullied by my in-laws.

99
00:09:10,258 --> 00:09:12,093
Wait! Hold on a second.

100
00:09:12,927 --> 00:09:15,013
What will you do
if my in-laws really bully me?

101
00:09:16,056 --> 00:09:18,850
I mean, just look at
how things are unfolding already.

102
00:09:18,933 --> 00:09:21,978
Let's say the Queen Mother
and I got into a fight.

103
00:09:22,062 --> 00:09:24,064
Would you take my side?

104
00:09:26,900 --> 00:09:29,652
Why aren't you answering?

105
00:09:30,445 --> 00:09:32,572
Will you take their side and not mine

106
00:09:32,655 --> 00:09:34,199
because they're your family?

107
00:09:39,746 --> 00:09:40,872
I will take your side.

108
00:09:49,380 --> 00:09:50,381
I must appear

109
00:09:51,591 --> 00:09:52,884
insanely infatuated with you…

110
00:10:01,935 --> 00:10:03,645
…for people to believe

111
00:10:05,522 --> 00:10:07,148
this absurd marriage is genuine.

112
00:10:16,741 --> 00:10:17,826
No, Your Royal Highness.

113
00:10:17,909 --> 00:10:19,911
You cannot let her sleep
in Anhwadang Hall.

114
00:10:19,994 --> 00:10:21,913
We have no choice
with the palace gates shut.

115
00:10:21,996 --> 00:10:24,082
We have the quarters
of the palace attendants.

116
00:10:24,165 --> 00:10:25,667
But she is not a palace attendant.

117
00:10:26,709 --> 00:10:28,461
I shall look for other vacant quarters--

118
00:10:28,545 --> 00:10:29,546
No need.

119
00:10:29,629 --> 00:10:31,881
Get her a change of clothes as well.

120
00:10:33,049 --> 00:10:34,050
Clothes?

121
00:10:34,676 --> 00:10:35,802
Huh?

122
00:10:36,469 --> 00:10:39,472
Can I get something that's 100% cotton?

123
00:10:42,016 --> 00:10:44,144
My skin's a little sensitive.

124
00:10:58,074 --> 00:10:59,868
Will you not even consider the sofa?

125
00:11:00,368 --> 00:11:03,079
No. This is perfectly fine.

126
00:11:08,334 --> 00:11:09,961
The sofa would be perfectly fine too.

127
00:11:10,044 --> 00:11:13,506
Then you should go. That'd be perfect.

128
00:11:53,046 --> 00:11:54,047
Stop!

129
00:11:59,594 --> 00:12:00,845
My goodness.

130
00:12:06,476 --> 00:12:08,228
-Oh, my.
-Your Royal Highness.

131
00:12:09,479 --> 00:12:10,688
Your Royal Highness!

132
00:12:10,772 --> 00:12:12,023
Stay still!

133
00:12:15,568 --> 00:12:17,028
Your Royal Highness.

134
00:12:19,447 --> 00:12:21,532
-Your Royal Highness!
-What? Stay still…

135
00:12:23,451 --> 00:12:24,744
My goodness.

136
00:12:24,827 --> 00:12:26,829
Do you know what time it is right now?

137
00:12:27,538 --> 00:12:29,707
It's unlike you to sleep in like this.

138
00:12:35,088 --> 00:12:37,382
Ms. Seong is already on her way to work.

139
00:12:37,465 --> 00:12:39,092
With a pep in her step, at that.

140
00:12:59,237 --> 00:13:00,822
