141
00:13:01,406 --> 00:13:02,573
No. Something wrong?

142
00:13:09,998 --> 00:13:12,542
Are you trying to show off
that you spent the night out?

143
00:13:12,625 --> 00:13:14,085
Did you not have time to change?

144
00:13:14,585 --> 00:13:17,005
I did have the time, but had no desire to.

145
00:13:17,672 --> 00:13:19,007
I wanted people to know

146
00:13:20,258 --> 00:13:21,509
I didn't go home last night.

147
00:13:22,969 --> 00:13:24,012
Oh.

148
00:13:38,568 --> 00:13:40,320
Are you quite pleased?

149
00:13:41,112 --> 00:13:44,532
Yes, I much prefer this over yakgwa.

150
00:13:48,494 --> 00:13:51,873
Did you sleep well last night?

151
00:13:58,212 --> 00:14:01,799
Did you dream about the late king again?

152
00:14:07,513 --> 00:14:08,514
Hmm.

153
00:14:23,738 --> 00:14:25,114
I am afraid.

154
00:14:27,742 --> 00:14:29,911
Do not worry,
Your Highness the Crown Prince.

155
00:14:30,703 --> 00:14:33,664
-You will have me by your side--
-You cannot, Your Royal Highness.

156
00:14:42,131 --> 00:14:43,132
Your Royal Highness.

157
00:14:44,092 --> 00:14:46,302
-The wedding rites are about to commence.
-So?

158
00:14:46,385 --> 00:14:48,930
You should take your place out there.

159
00:14:52,558 --> 00:14:54,560
Should His Majesty learn of this…

160
00:14:58,314 --> 00:15:01,442
you will be punished
for dishonoring the Crown Prince.

161
00:15:01,526 --> 00:15:03,236
Are you prepared for that?

162
00:15:05,863 --> 00:15:06,864
Your Royal Highness!

163
00:15:11,160 --> 00:15:12,954
I clearly gave you a chance.

164
00:15:14,288 --> 00:15:15,832
Whatever happens from here on…

165
00:15:18,251 --> 00:15:19,252
you will have to…

166
00:15:21,129 --> 00:15:22,380
deal with it yourself.

167
00:15:27,760 --> 00:15:29,428
I am scared.

168
00:15:32,473 --> 00:15:35,476
Ah. Do not worry, Your Majesty.

169
00:15:35,977 --> 00:15:40,106
You will always have
your grandfather by your side.

170
00:15:43,025 --> 00:15:44,026
Go on.

171
00:15:56,956 --> 00:15:58,791
FAMILY APPRECIATION
MONTH EVENT REPORT

172
00:16:20,521 --> 00:16:22,481
A ROYAL SCANDAL?
SEONG HUIJU HIT THE JACKPOT…

173
00:16:23,733 --> 00:16:27,445
