the situation closely.

179
00:16:43,586 --> 00:16:45,922
"Guys, maybe she has something on him?

180
00:16:46,005 --> 00:16:48,841
Why else would he date a commoner?"

181
00:16:48,925 --> 00:16:50,593
Why do you think, loser?

182
00:16:50,676 --> 00:16:52,845
Because I'm worth dating. That's why.

183
00:16:53,512 --> 00:16:55,264
-You little…
-Here.

184
00:16:55,890 --> 00:16:59,518
The top five trending keywords
are all about you.

185
00:16:59,602 --> 00:17:01,979
Your hotel outfit is already sold out.

186
00:17:02,772 --> 00:17:03,773
Really?

187
00:17:05,524 --> 00:17:06,651
Call the PR team.

188
00:17:06,734 --> 00:17:08,694
The PR team? Why?

189
00:17:08,778 --> 00:17:09,779
Why else?

190
00:17:10,446 --> 00:17:13,449
It's time to take back
the number-one spot in sales.

191
00:17:14,575 --> 00:17:16,535
How can you even
think about that right now?

192
00:17:17,828 --> 00:17:19,205
It's marriage, not retirement.

193
00:17:23,668 --> 00:17:25,753
Oh. Jeongwoo?

194
00:17:26,420 --> 00:17:27,421
Hello, sir.

195
00:17:28,172 --> 00:17:30,383
-Isn't he so handsome?
-Super handsome!

196
00:17:30,466 --> 00:17:33,094
This is my first time seeing
Prime Minister Min in person.

197
00:17:33,177 --> 00:17:35,304
He looks like a total celebrity.

198
00:17:35,388 --> 00:17:37,098
Right. But what's he doing here?

199
00:17:37,181 --> 00:17:38,307
Maybe because of the scandal?

200
00:17:38,391 --> 00:17:40,851
-Oh! That must be--
-Why is no one working?

201
00:17:43,688 --> 00:17:46,148
You're really going to marry him?

202
00:17:46,899 --> 00:17:48,526
-Yeah.
-His Royal Highness?

203
00:17:48,609 --> 00:17:50,027
Yeah.

204
00:17:50,111 --> 00:17:51,737
I thought you two had just met.

205
00:17:52,363 --> 00:17:53,823
Can't you just stick to dating?

206
00:17:53,906 --> 00:17:56,284
But I want to be with him all the time.

207
00:17:57,118 --> 00:17:59,787
-Huiju…
-I want to wake up next to him

208
00:18:00,413 --> 00:18:01,455
every day.

209
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:06,127
I hear the royal family

210
00:18:06,210 --> 00:18:08,629
wants to marry him off to someone else.

211
00:18:10,715 --> 00:18:14,051
That's why I have to marry him right now.

212
00:18:14,635 --> 00:18:16,053
While you're the Prime Minister.

213
00:18:21,267 --> 00:18:22,602
I need you to get

214
00:18:24,020 --> 00:18:25,021
my marriage approved.

215
00:18:34,405 --> 00:18:37,325
We're planning to invite
the top 300 patrons in the country.

216
00:18:37,908 --> 00:18:40,161
-What are the criteria?
-Your Royal Highness.

217
00:18:54,717 --> 00:18:57,136
The Queen Mother has taken to her sickbed.

218
00:18:57,219 --> 00:18:58,512
All of a sudden?

219
00:18:58,596 --> 00:19:01,057
Perhaps it's a ploy
to prevent an official statement.

220
00:19:01,140 --> 00:19:04,143
The palace cannot speak of celebrations
while a royal elder lies ill.

221
00:19:11,317 --> 00:19:12,818
JUNIOR ALUM

222
00:19:14,028 --> 00:19:15,196
Understood. You may leave.

223
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:22,328
Your Royal Highness!

224
00:19:23,829 --> 00:19:25,456
I hear you fine. Lower your voice.

225
00:19:26,290 --> 00:19:27,416
Did you read the article?

226
00:19:29,293 --> 00:19:30,670
Right before it was pulled.

227
00:19:31,462 --> 00:19:33,214
It was taken down at lightning speed.

228
00:19:33,297 --> 00:19:35,091
The Queen Mother has been very busy.

229
00:19:35,174 --> 00:19:37,176
I guess even nobles can move quickly

230
00:19:37,259 --> 00:19:38,636
when they want to.

231
00:19:42,973 --> 00:19:43,974
Seong Huiju?

232
00:19:44,517 --> 00:19:45,518
Oh?

233
00:19:46,727 --> 00:19:47,978
You sly fox!

234
00:19:48,062 --> 00:19:50,022
You dare try to seduce His Royal Highness!

235
00:19:51,065 --> 00:19:52,692
-"Fox"?
-Yeah, you fox!

236
00:19:53,442 --> 00:19:56,278
-Oh, my gosh!
-Stay away from His Royal Highness!

237
00:19:56,362 --> 00:19:58,906
-Get lost!
-Hey, good job.

238
00:20:00,825 --> 00:20:01,909
Seong Huiju?

239
00:20:01,992 --> 00:20:03,661
Should we? Should we not?

240
00:20:04,328 --> 00:20:05,413
Come here, you brats.

241
00:20:05,496 --> 00:20:08,290
-We could throw them all.
-"Come here, you brats!"

242
00:20:10,418 --> 00:20:11,961
Get over here now!

243
00:20:27,727 --> 00:20:28,728
Your Royal Highness.

244
00:20:31,355 --> 00:20:32,565
What is all that?

245
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:34,525
Is it not obvious? These are your duties.

246
00:20:34,608 --> 00:20:36,152
-All of it?
-All of it.

247
00:20:38,195 --> 00:20:40,698
-That cannot be true.
-It most certainly is.

248
00:20:40,781 --> 00:20:44,368
These are the duties you are
to carry out on His Majesty's behalf.

249
00:20:45,035 --> 00:20:48,330
These are the Queen Mother's… Goodness.
This stack is quite heavy.

250
00:20:48,414 --> 00:20:51,542
These are the Queen Mother's duties
you are to carry out

251
00:20:52,251 --> 00:20:53,544
in her absence.

252
00:20:53,627 --> 00:20:56,338
And these are your duties
that accumulated while you were away.

253
00:20:57,006 --> 00:20:58,716
-You got this.
-Get out.

254
00:20:58,799 --> 00:21:00,092
Yes, sir.

255
00:21:00,676 --> 00:21:02,720
Let's go. Off we go.

256
00:21:06,849 --> 00:21:10,102
You little brats should be in school
with your noses in books.

257
00:21:10,186 --> 00:21:11,687
Eyes down!

258
00:21:12,897 --> 00:21:15,483
Does Prince I-AN put food on your table?

259
00:21:15,566 --> 00:21:17,693
He may not feed us, but he gives us money.

260
00:21:17,777 --> 00:21:20,196
-Right.
-We're royal scholarship students.

261
00:21:20,988 --> 00:21:22,948
That money was for your studies.

262
00:21:23,032 --> 00:21:26,160
Do you think he wanted you to spend
that money buying eggs to throw?

263
00:21:26,827 --> 00:21:27,953
And you, Hyerin.

264
00:21:28,496 --> 00:21:30,706
Why did you assume I seduced him?

265
00:21:30,790 --> 00:21:31,791
Isn't it obvious?

266
00:21:31,874 --> 00:21:33,083
Why, you little…

267
00:21:33,167 --> 00:21:35,920
So young and already full of prejudice.

268
00:21:36,003 --> 00:21:37,880
If I had it my way,

269
00:21:38,631 --> 00:21:42,468
I'd give you hell and take legal action
for pulling something like this…

270
00:21:44,011 --> 00:21:45,179
Come here.

271
00:21:46,305 --> 00:21:47,556
But right now,

272
00:21:48,140 --> 00:21:50,559
your big sis here has
a major undertaking ahead of her.

273
00:21:51,227 --> 00:21:53,354
So I'll let it slide just this once.

274
00:21:54,063 --> 00:21:55,064
Got it?

275
00:21:56,565 --> 00:21:58,400
-Answer me!
-Yes, ma'am!

276
00:22:01,987 --> 00:22:03,364
Off you go.

277
00:22:03,447 --> 00:22:04,824
Almighty God.

278
00:22:05,991 --> 00:22:08,160
Please have mercy on us,

279
00:22:09,161 --> 00:22:10,788
forgive us our sins,

280
00:22:11,872 --> 00:22:15,543
and bring us to everlasting life.

281
00:22:17,044 --> 00:22:18,045
Amen.

282
00:22:21,841 --> 00:22:23,092
Amen.

283
00:22:25,302 --> 00:22:27,388
You said you couldn't come for a while.

284
00:22:28,681 --> 00:22:31,809
I heard my friend is getting married,
so I came to pray.

285
00:22:33,143 --> 00:22:36,438
That friend is very lucky to have you
praying for her happiness.

286
00:22:37,022 --> 00:22:38,023
I'm not so sure.

287
00:22:38,983 --> 00:22:40,317
I prayed for something sinful.

288
00:22:41,819 --> 00:22:42,987
Something sinful?

289
00:22:44,905 --> 00:22:46,115
I do not feel inclined

290
00:22:47,032 --> 00:22:48,367
to congratulate her.

291
00:23:01,255 --> 00:23:03,924
But I don't want to stop her either.

292
00:23:10,097 --> 00:23:11,640
Even if I don't think it's right…

293
00:23:12,558 --> 00:23:13,976
Damn it.

294
00:23:14,059 --> 00:23:16,228
Where did that punk hide it?

295
00:23:16,812 --> 00:23:18,522
If that's what she wants…

296
00:23:20,441 --> 00:23:22,276
-Ma'am.
-Hey, Jeongwoo.

297
00:23:22,359 --> 00:23:23,736
Are you running an errand?

298
00:23:23,819 --> 00:23:26,322
Yes.

299
00:23:26,405 --> 00:23:28,324
Principal Kim was looking for you earlier.

300
00:23:28,407 --> 00:23:29,658
Did you see him?

301
00:23:30,659 --> 00:23:31,869
…I have to let her.

302
00:23:32,578 --> 00:23:33,787
Found it.

303
00:23:36,498 --> 00:23:37,499
Got it.

304
00:24:04,526 --> 00:24:07,738
I mean, how did those brats
even get past security?

305
00:24:08,656 --> 00:24:11,450
You have to hand it
to the high schoolers in this country.

306
00:24:20,918 --> 00:24:21,919
Father?

307
00:24:34,098 --> 00:24:37,142
Can I get you anything?

308
00:24:40,187 --> 00:24:41,355
Don't bother. Sit.

309
00:24:50,239 --> 00:24:51,657
About that scandal…

310
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:53,409
No need to explain.

311
00:24:54,868 --> 00:24:58,706
-You're not curious?
-There's nothing to be curious about.

312
00:24:58,789 --> 00:24:59,790
I'm sure

313
00:25:00,290 --> 00:25:02,584
it's just a cheap stunt
you pulled for attention.

314
00:25:05,379 --> 00:25:06,547
Then why are you here?

315
00:25:11,135 --> 00:25:12,136
It's nearly…

316
00:25:13,637 --> 00:25:15,180
Taeju's mother's death anniversary.

317
00:25:17,016 --> 00:25:18,934
I was wondering if you even remembered.

318
00:25:22,646 --> 00:25:23,647
Ma'am.

319
00:25:27,818 --> 00:25:30,029
She's been standing
outside the house for hours,

320
00:25:30,654 --> 00:25:32,489
but she refuses to talk.

321
00:25:33,073 --> 00:25:36,076
Then you should've reported her
to the police, not brought her inside.

322
00:25:36,702 --> 00:25:37,828
Send her away.

323
00:25:37,911 --> 00:25:40,831
How can we just send away a child
in the middle of the night?

324
00:25:43,083 --> 00:25:45,669
Little one, are you lost?

325
00:25:48,213 --> 00:25:49,381
What's your name?

326
00:25:53,594 --> 00:25:55,012
You don't want to say?

327
00:25:58,348 --> 00:25:59,683
I am

328
00:26:00,267 --> 00:26:01,935
Lee Jooyeon's daughter.

329
00:26:07,566 --> 00:26:08,734
You're my dad…

330
00:26:09,651 --> 00:26:10,652
aren't you?

331
00:26:23,916 --> 00:26:25,709
-Honey! Honey!
-Mom!

332
00:26:25,793 --> 00:26:28,045
-Ma'am! Wake up, ma'am!
-Honey!

333
00:26:28,128 --> 00:26:30,422
-Honey!
-Ma'am!

334
00:26:30,964 --> 00:26:33,133
-Ma'am! Oh, dear goodness!
-Mom, wake up!

335
00:26:33,217 --> 00:26:35,719
Since the day your mother abandoned you…

336
00:26:35,803 --> 00:26:37,096
-Ma'am.
-Mommy!

337
00:26:37,179 --> 00:26:38,972
…our lives fell into despair.

338
00:26:46,980 --> 00:26:48,440
CERTIFICATE OF AWARD

339
00:26:48,524 --> 00:26:50,818
Buy me a bike too.

340
00:26:50,901 --> 00:26:53,570
The same one as Taeju.

341
00:26:56,198 --> 00:26:58,534
You dared to be greedy…

342
00:26:59,118 --> 00:27:00,327
REPORT CARD

343
00:27:01,328 --> 00:27:02,996
I want a building too.

344
00:27:03,080 --> 00:27:04,915
One that's taller than Taeju's.

345
00:27:04,998 --> 00:27:06,250
So greedy…

346
00:27:07,251 --> 00:27:08,252
STOCK PRICE ANALYSIS

347
00:27:08,335 --> 00:27:10,003
Amend your will, Father.

348
00:27:10,671 --> 00:27:11,922
In my favor.

349
00:27:12,005 --> 00:27:13,632
Your greed was relentless!

350
00:27:20,305 --> 00:27:22,057
Keep your hands off the company.

351
00:27:22,140 --> 00:27:23,183
And if I don't?

352
00:27:23,267 --> 00:27:24,893
I'll have no choice but to act.

353
00:27:26,812 --> 00:27:28,981
-What? Are you going to disown me?
-Why not?

354
00:27:29,064 --> 00:27:30,274
Listen, Mr. Seong Hyeonguk.

355
00:27:30,357 --> 00:27:32,109
You dare call your father by his name?

356
00:27:32,192 --> 00:27:33,694
You just said you'd disown me.

357
00:27:34,528 --> 00:27:36,113
Then you wouldn't be my dad anyway.

358
00:27:37,614 --> 00:27:40,492
So, Mr. Seong Hyeonguk, to summarize,

359
00:27:40,576 --> 00:27:42,077
I shouldn't bother acting out

360
00:27:42,160 --> 00:27:45,163
because it'll all be
Taeju's in the end, right?

361
00:27:45,664 --> 00:27:47,416
Seong Taeju will be the ultimate winner.

362
00:27:47,499 --> 00:27:49,543
Taeju is so awesome!

363
00:27:50,043 --> 00:27:51,253
That's the gist.

364
00:27:51,920 --> 00:27:52,921
Right?

365
00:27:53,881 --> 00:27:56,800
I should just kill Taeju
and secure my spot in hell.

366
00:27:56,884 --> 00:27:57,968
Seong Huiju!

367
00:27:58,051 --> 00:28:00,929
Anyone who ever tried to pick a fight
with me was exactly like you.

368
00:28:01,722 --> 00:28:04,141
They'd stack the deck
so they couldn't help but win,

369
00:28:04,224 --> 00:28:06,351
and put me in a spot
where I was bound to lose.

370
00:28:08,103 --> 00:28:09,438
I guess they weren't confident

371
00:28:10,063 --> 00:28:11,523
they could win on equal terms.

372
00:28:16,153 --> 00:28:17,154
But you know what?

373
00:28:17,654 --> 00:28:18,989
It's fine.

374
00:28:19,615 --> 00:28:21,366
I'm used to going up against

375
00:28:22,451 --> 00:28:23,493
people like that.

376
00:28:23,577 --> 00:28:24,995
You just won't quit.

377
00:28:25,078 --> 00:28:26,079
I wish you…

378
00:28:26,955 --> 00:28:27,956
all the best.

379
00:28:29,374 --> 00:28:30,918
Though I'm sure you'll lose anyway.

380
00:29:07,579 --> 00:29:09,748
PRINCE

381
00:29:21,051 --> 00:29:22,594
Sorry for hanging up on you earlier--

382
00:29:22,678 --> 00:29:23,929
Are you okay?

383
00:29:27,432 --> 00:29:28,600
Are you all right?

384
00:29:32,104 --> 00:29:33,897
Seong Huiju, can you not hear me?

385
00:29:35,941 --> 00:29:37,776
Can I call you back tomorrow?

386
00:29:38,694 --> 00:29:39,695
What?

387
00:29:40,404 --> 00:29:41,738
I'm a little busy right now.

388
00:29:43,073 --> 00:29:44,157
I'll call you tomorrow.

389
00:29:59,881 --> 00:30:02,134
JUNIOR ALUM

390
00:30:43,508 --> 00:30:46,011
CERTIFICATE OF AWARD

391
00:30:59,107 --> 00:31:00,108
HAPPY BIRTHDAY, TAEJU

392
00:31:00,192 --> 00:31:01,818
HOPE YOU GROW UP
STRONG AND HEALTHY

393
00:31:08,575 --> 00:31:10,577
Buy me a bike too.

394
00:31:11,578 --> 00:31:13,955
The same one as Taeju.

395
00:31:29,137 --> 00:31:30,597
REPORT CARD

396
00:31:37,312 --> 00:31:38,730
I want a building too.

397
00:31:39,648 --> 00:31:41,024
One that's taller than Taeju's.

398
00:31:48,323 --> 00:31:49,991
Amend your will, Father.

399
00:31:50,575 --> 00:31:51,827
In my favor.

400
00:32:08,885 --> 00:32:09,970
Who is it?

401
00:32:13,849 --> 00:32:15,183
Someone lost their damn mind.

402
00:32:15,767 --> 00:32:17,310
Who the hell is it at this hour…

403
00:32:21,106 --> 00:32:22,274
Damn it.

404
00:32:37,914 --> 00:32:38,915
Your Royal Highness?

405
00:32:39,624 --> 00:32:41,710
Wait, are we playing hide and seek?

406
00:32:43,712 --> 00:32:44,796
What are you doing here?

407
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,631
Wait, are you allowed to be here?

408
00:32:46,715 --> 00:32:49,217
Hold on. Did anyone see you?

409
00:32:49,301 --> 00:32:50,427
Where's Aide Choi?

410
00:32:51,136 --> 00:32:52,304
You play baseball at home?

411
00:32:56,600 --> 00:33:00,270
I have one too many enemies, you see.

412
00:33:05,650 --> 00:33:06,651
Oh.

413
00:33:06,735 --> 00:33:07,736
Wait.

414
00:33:08,361 --> 00:33:11,198
How did you even get here?

415
00:33:11,281 --> 00:33:12,908
Wait, did you come here alone?

416
00:33:12,991 --> 00:33:13,992
Yeah.

417
00:33:15,118 --> 00:33:16,494
You can't just…

418
00:33:21,875 --> 00:33:23,084
Let me get this straight.

419
00:33:24,211 --> 00:33:25,962
You picked these up yourself?

420
00:33:37,933 --> 00:33:39,017
THE SEONG HUIJU COMBO

421
00:33:39,100 --> 00:33:40,310
I will have this one.

422
00:33:42,270 --> 00:33:43,897
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

423
00:33:45,106 --> 00:33:47,067
"Seduce the Prince" Seong Huiju Combo.

424
00:33:48,026 --> 00:33:49,027
It seemed popular.

425
00:34:11,716 --> 00:34:12,717
Seriously?

426
00:34:13,218 --> 00:34:16,221
Couldn't you have left
after you finished your work?

427
00:34:25,605 --> 00:34:27,565
-What is it?
-Just a bit amazed.

428
00:34:28,358 --> 00:34:29,484
By what?

429
00:34:30,277 --> 00:34:31,820
I came because you sounded so down.

430
00:34:32,612 --> 00:34:35,365
But seeing you eat,
you seem perfectly fine.

431
00:34:41,162 --> 00:34:42,289
I was a little down.

432
00:34:42,372 --> 00:34:45,417
I was dragged
through the mud all day, you see.

433
00:34:46,376 --> 00:34:48,962
I was barraged
with hate comments on social media.

434
00:34:49,045 --> 00:34:51,548
My father suddenly threatened
to disown me.

435
00:34:51,631 --> 00:34:52,632
Oh, that's right.

436
00:34:53,133 --> 00:34:56,636
I even got egged by your fans today.

437
00:34:56,720 --> 00:34:59,347
I totally forgot to ask
if those eggs were antibiotic-free.

438
00:35:00,015 --> 00:35:01,182
You got "egged"?

439
00:35:01,266 --> 00:35:02,767
Yeah. Two eggs, no less.

440
00:35:02,851 --> 00:35:06,187
Those little pip-squeaks were
so damn strong for no reason.

441
00:35:07,272 --> 00:35:08,690
-It still hurts.
-Here?

442
00:35:08,773 --> 00:35:10,275
Yeah. Just downstairs.

443
00:35:12,027 --> 00:35:13,612
Are you hurt?

444
00:35:17,115 --> 00:35:18,158
Are you hurt anywhere?

445
00:35:53,985 --> 00:35:55,403
An investigation is required.

446
00:36:00,617 --> 00:36:01,951
They're coming right now?

447
00:36:02,035 --> 00:36:03,620
That's what I said. Now, move it!

448
00:36:11,544 --> 00:36:13,546
She will be staying here
for the time being.

449
00:36:20,470 --> 00:36:22,972
She has been receiving
a troublesome amount of attention.

450
00:36:24,057 --> 00:36:25,350
I was concerned.

451
00:36:26,101 --> 00:36:27,227
So you were…

452
00:36:28,353 --> 00:36:29,938
concerned.

453
00:36:30,730 --> 00:36:31,815
And my instructions?

454
00:36:31,898 --> 00:36:34,150
Everything is ready, Your Royal Highness.

455
00:36:41,032 --> 00:36:42,033
Oh!

456
00:36:49,165 --> 00:36:50,750
Maybe that's a bit too close?

457
00:37:05,640 --> 00:37:07,559
Please make yourself at home.

458
00:37:09,018 --> 00:37:11,479
What should I call you?

459
00:37:12,272 --> 00:37:13,857
-Pardon?
-How should I address you?

460
00:37:13,940 --> 00:37:15,775
Uh…

461
00:37:17,736 --> 00:37:20,864
I am Yeongmun of the Kim Family,
the steward of this residence.

462
00:37:20,947 --> 00:37:23,825
Feel free to call me Steward Kim.

463
00:37:25,201 --> 00:37:27,078
Steward? Hmm.

464
00:37:27,912 --> 00:37:28,913
Yes, ma'am.

465
00:37:29,622 --> 00:37:30,707
Steward.

466
00:37:32,667 --> 00:37:34,586
It's late, so I will leave you to rest.

467
00:37:34,669 --> 00:37:38,339
I will give you a proper tour
of the property tomorrow.

468
00:37:38,423 --> 00:37:39,674
All right.

469
00:37:45,180 --> 00:37:46,306
Just a second.

470
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:51,186
How shall I address you?

471
00:37:51,811 --> 00:37:53,188
Ah.

472
00:37:57,901 --> 00:38:01,780
I prefer Ms. Seong or Executive Director,
but you can call me by my name.

473
00:38:01,863 --> 00:38:04,365
You're not my employee, after all.

474
00:38:07,160 --> 00:38:08,161
Then, I shall

475
00:38:09,162 --> 00:38:10,455
address you as Your Ladyship.

476
00:38:11,998 --> 00:38:13,666
"Your Ladyship"?

477
00:38:14,876 --> 00:38:16,044
Well then.

478
00:38:27,013 --> 00:38:28,807
I was at the palace yesterday,

479
00:38:28,890 --> 00:38:31,226
and today, the prince's private residence.

480
00:38:40,568 --> 00:38:41,820
Yes, Your Royal Highness.

481
00:38:42,403 --> 00:38:43,571
Do you like your room?

482
00:38:44,906 --> 00:38:45,907
I mean, it's nice.

483
00:38:46,407 --> 00:38:48,409
It feels like I'm on
a historical drama set.

484
00:38:49,619 --> 00:38:51,287
Why aren't you sleeping?

485
00:38:51,830 --> 00:38:52,956
I have some work to do.

486
00:38:55,959 --> 00:38:57,210
Do you want me to help?

487
00:39:52,307 --> 00:39:54,893
So am I really going to live here now?

488
00:39:56,352 --> 00:39:58,104
Well, it's just that

489
00:39:58,646 --> 00:40:01,065
I'm quite an independent woman.

490
00:40:01,566 --> 00:40:03,401
I find this bustling environment…

491
00:40:04,319 --> 00:40:05,695
a bit bothersome, shall I say?

492
00:40:06,195 --> 00:40:07,739
It's so far from work too.

493
00:40:09,532 --> 00:40:11,117
Shouldn't you be more "bothered"

494
00:40:11,868 --> 00:40:15,288
if I were to leave you in harm's way
when I'm supposedly infatuated with you?

495
00:40:15,371 --> 00:40:16,581
Commute aside.

496
00:40:16,664 --> 00:40:18,291
Okay.

497
00:40:24,422 --> 00:40:25,465
By the way…

498
00:40:27,216 --> 00:40:28,509
You wanted to help.

499
00:40:28,593 --> 00:40:29,594
Is this you helping?

500
00:40:30,511 --> 00:40:32,889
I don't know anything
about the royal ancestral rites.

501
00:40:33,389 --> 00:40:35,350
I've never even attended
any of my family's.

502
00:40:43,942 --> 00:40:45,234
What do you want to know?

503
00:40:47,987 --> 00:40:49,155
Why are you marrying me?

504
00:40:50,698 --> 00:40:52,909
Isn't it a bit late to be asking that?

505
00:40:52,992 --> 00:40:55,495
We only made the decision yesterday.

506
00:40:55,578 --> 00:40:57,789
Why can't I be a little curious today?

507
00:40:59,707 --> 00:41:00,792
You have a lot of money.

508
00:41:01,459 --> 00:41:03,211
The richest in the country, no less.

509
00:41:05,546 --> 00:41:07,006
Is that your reason?

510
00:41:07,090 --> 00:41:08,424
The most important reason.

511
00:41:08,508 --> 00:41:11,094
It would help the royal family,
always under fire

512
00:41:11,177 --> 00:41:13,096
for squandering taxpayers' money.

513
00:41:15,098 --> 00:41:16,891
And what a noble reason it is.

514
00:41:17,392 --> 00:41:18,893
Second.

515
00:41:21,896 --> 00:41:22,939
Beauty.

516
00:41:23,940 --> 00:41:24,983
"Beauty"?

517
00:41:25,566 --> 00:41:28,361
Oh, I guess that finally broke through.

518
00:41:30,405 --> 00:41:31,990
-Third.
-What? What now?

519
00:41:32,073 --> 00:41:33,658
Because my family doesn't overstep?

520
00:41:33,741 --> 00:41:35,785
If I say I wish to ascend the throne,

521
00:41:37,996 --> 00:41:40,123
all would condemn me and hurl insults.

522
00:41:44,460 --> 00:41:45,461
But I believe

523
00:41:46,713 --> 00:41:47,922
you would understand me.

524
00:42:11,988 --> 00:42:14,323
The Inner Court Banquet
is still some time away.

525
00:42:14,407 --> 00:42:17,160
Yet I am already being pressed
to make a decision.

526
00:42:17,243 --> 00:42:19,203
It appears they are quite anxious,

527
00:42:19,287 --> 00:42:21,414
as they need to finalize
the guest list soon.

528
00:42:21,497 --> 00:42:25,084
Does Your Majesty have any criteria
in mind for the guest list?

529
00:42:25,668 --> 00:42:26,794
I'm not sure.

530
00:42:30,214 --> 00:42:33,426
Those with exemplary character,
admirable talents,

531
00:42:34,969 --> 00:42:36,387
and innate nobility?

532
00:42:39,390 --> 00:42:41,100
Would that suffice?

533
00:42:51,402 --> 00:42:53,321
I must cancel today's itinerary.

534
00:42:54,155 --> 00:42:55,364
Pardon?

535
00:42:55,448 --> 00:42:56,574
But they already--

536
00:42:56,657 --> 00:42:58,076
Surely there should be no issue.

537
00:43:01,287 --> 00:43:02,997
I am indisposed, after all.

538
00:43:18,387 --> 00:43:20,264
Your Ladyship, please wake up.

539
00:43:25,311 --> 00:43:26,604
Your Ladyship, wake up.

540
00:43:28,272 --> 00:43:29,273
Wait, hold on.

541
00:43:31,025 --> 00:43:33,319
How dare you storm in here! Hey, you!

542
00:43:33,402 --> 00:43:34,487
Youngseon!

543
00:43:34,570 --> 00:43:36,948
Why that little prick…

544
00:43:39,117 --> 00:43:40,284
What in the world?

545
00:43:52,672 --> 00:43:53,673
What's this about?

546
00:43:53,756 --> 00:43:57,468
Cooperate with the Junghwajeon Hall
fire investigation, please.

547
00:43:57,552 --> 00:43:58,970
"Cooperate"?

548
00:44:02,640 --> 00:44:04,016
At the Royal Birthday Banquet,

549
00:44:04,892 --> 00:44:07,645
you entered a restricted area
of the palace, didn't you?

550
00:44:08,771 --> 00:44:10,731
I did get lost at one point.

551
00:44:11,649 --> 00:44:12,650
But what about it?

552
00:44:13,401 --> 00:44:15,778
Are you suggesting
I started the fire or something?

553
00:44:16,362 --> 00:44:17,822
Nothing has been ruled out yet.

554
00:44:18,990 --> 00:44:22,618
You'll need to give a detailed account
of what you did and who you met there.

555
00:44:23,369 --> 00:44:25,204
What exactly am I supposed to explain?

556
00:44:29,125 --> 00:44:30,668
What was that?

557
00:44:30,751 --> 00:44:31,752
You stay here.

558
00:44:32,503 --> 00:44:34,964
You've publicly stated,
"The royal family is a money pit.

559
00:44:35,464 --> 00:44:38,593
Someone should abolish the Crown.
Let's bring out the guillotine."

560
00:44:39,135 --> 00:44:40,136
Is that correct?

561
00:44:43,890 --> 00:44:44,891
Do you have a warrant?

562
00:44:47,185 --> 00:44:50,146
Under the Royalty
and Specialist Protection Law,

563
00:44:50,229 --> 00:44:53,649
suspects of royal threats
may be investigated prior to a warrant.

564
00:44:54,817 --> 00:44:55,860
Get started.

565
00:44:56,819 --> 00:44:58,613
Hold on. Take your shoes off.

566
00:44:59,780 --> 00:45:01,324
No, you can't take that!

567
00:45:07,496 --> 00:45:09,540
What do you think you're doing?

568
00:45:09,624 --> 00:45:11,584
-Hold on a second.
-You can't take this!

569
00:45:11,667 --> 00:45:13,377
-What are you doing?
-Move!

570
00:45:13,461 --> 00:45:16,130
-Is this really necessary?
-Please step aside.

571
00:45:17,590 --> 00:45:18,799
What are you doing?

572
00:45:18,883 --> 00:45:20,843
-This is insane.
-Why are you doing this?

573
00:45:27,892 --> 00:45:29,060
Damn it. What now?

574
00:45:29,143 --> 00:45:30,853
Gosh, you're working so hard.

575
00:45:30,937 --> 00:45:32,021
Have you eaten yet?

576
00:45:32,104 --> 00:45:33,731
-You need to eat something.
-I'm fine.

577
00:45:33,814 --> 00:45:35,483
Let's fill that belly first.

578
00:45:35,566 --> 00:45:39,111
This is His Royal Highness's favorite,
so let's have a taste.

579
00:45:39,195 --> 00:45:40,571
Come on. Take a seat.

580
00:45:40,655 --> 00:45:43,699
Sit down. Let's have a bite while we chat.

581
00:45:44,200 --> 00:45:45,868
Go on. Just try one.

582
00:45:48,913 --> 00:45:52,041
Your Ladyship,
you need to eat something too.

583
00:45:52,124 --> 00:45:53,918
Can't be questioned on an empty stomach.

584
00:45:54,001 --> 00:45:55,795
-Go on. It's still warm.
-No thanks.

585
00:45:55,878 --> 00:45:57,088
-Come on!
-Stop it.

586
00:45:57,672 --> 00:45:59,215
I'm calling His Royal Highness.

587
00:46:01,175 --> 00:46:02,677
Why isn't he picking up?

588
00:46:03,886 --> 00:46:05,137
He probably won't answer.

589
00:46:05,805 --> 00:46:06,806
What?

590
00:46:06,889 --> 00:46:09,308
Cell phones are not allowed
during the ritual.

591
00:46:10,351 --> 00:46:11,352
Ritual?

592
00:46:11,978 --> 00:46:13,062
As in ancestral rites?

593
00:46:34,583 --> 00:46:36,585
Ms. Do. You're running, right?

594
00:46:36,669 --> 00:46:38,504
Yes, I'm running.

595
00:46:38,587 --> 00:46:40,423
What a hell of a way to spend the weekend.

596
00:46:40,506 --> 00:46:42,883
What choice do I have?
You're the only one I can trust.

597
00:46:42,967 --> 00:46:44,302
Forget all that.

598
00:46:44,385 --> 00:46:46,095
Prepare to give me a hefty bonus.

599
00:46:46,679 --> 00:46:47,722
Hang up now.

600
00:46:50,182 --> 00:46:51,183
I got this.

601
00:46:53,060 --> 00:46:54,312
She won't get in.

602
00:46:54,395 --> 00:46:55,771
Why not?

603
00:46:55,855 --> 00:46:57,106
She's a civilian.

604
00:46:57,982 --> 00:47:00,901
Civilians may enter Jongmyo Shrine
only on special days.

605
00:47:02,862 --> 00:47:03,863
Come on.

606
00:47:05,823 --> 00:47:07,950
Oh. Oh!

607
00:47:08,034 --> 00:47:09,493
Huh?

608
00:47:09,577 --> 00:47:11,746
ROYAL PROTECTION BRANCH

609
00:47:29,430 --> 00:47:30,431
Shall we?

610
00:47:42,151 --> 00:47:43,444
-Hurry up, ma'am.
-Hold on…

611
00:47:44,278 --> 00:47:46,197
My goodness.

612
00:47:47,156 --> 00:47:49,241
Wait. I can't believe this.

613
00:47:49,325 --> 00:47:51,285
-Please let me in this once.
-No, you can't.

614
00:47:51,369 --> 00:47:53,120
I'm from Castle Beauty.

615
00:47:53,204 --> 00:47:54,830
I need to see His Royal Highness.

616
00:47:54,914 --> 00:47:55,998
We already told you no.

617
00:47:56,499 --> 00:47:57,792
Just leave already!

618
00:47:57,875 --> 00:47:59,585
How can I when I know he's in there?

619
00:48:04,131 --> 00:48:05,674
Ms. Do!

620
00:48:06,175 --> 00:48:08,803
Ms. Do!

621
00:48:09,387 --> 00:48:11,764
Ms. Do! Oh, Ms. Do!

622
00:48:11,847 --> 00:48:13,265
Ms. Do…

623
00:48:17,144 --> 00:48:18,813
We come by order of the Grand Prince.

624
00:48:18,896 --> 00:48:21,649
GRAND PRINCE I-AN

625
00:48:41,252 --> 00:48:42,253
Good heavens!

626
00:48:44,755 --> 00:48:45,840
That…

627
00:48:45,923 --> 00:48:47,800
Isn't that the Grand Prince's hopae?

628
00:48:47,883 --> 00:48:49,885
Why was that precious thing in the toilet?

629
00:48:51,512 --> 00:48:53,097
-Steward Kim.
-Yes?

630
00:48:55,891 --> 00:48:57,268
Please take it to Jongmyo.

631
00:48:58,227 --> 00:49:00,479
-Pardon?
-Just in case.

632
00:49:01,856 --> 00:49:02,898
I'm counting on you.

633
00:49:03,607 --> 00:49:04,608
You got this!

634
00:49:07,862 --> 00:49:08,863
Good luck!

635
00:49:10,239 --> 00:49:11,323
Good? Step aside.

636
00:49:11,407 --> 00:49:13,951
I knew it!
You could've just let me pass earlier!

637
00:49:20,666 --> 00:49:22,418
Where are you going? It's this way.

638
00:49:24,044 --> 00:49:25,921
That bonus better be a generous one.

639
00:49:26,672 --> 00:49:27,715
I'm so exhausted.

640
00:50:19,683 --> 00:50:22,144
Oh, dear. He can't step out
while the ritual is underway.

641
00:50:22,228 --> 00:50:24,647
It's already started.

642
00:50:33,113 --> 00:50:34,156
Oh.

643
00:50:35,491 --> 00:50:37,618
-If he can't leave…
-Yes?

644
00:50:38,118 --> 00:50:39,495
…we can go in instead.

645
00:50:40,788 --> 00:50:41,997
What?

646
00:50:54,218 --> 00:50:55,219
Huh?

647
00:50:55,302 --> 00:50:57,054
-We need to go.
-What?

648
00:50:57,137 --> 00:50:59,139
-We need to go.
-Pardon?

649
00:50:59,223 --> 00:51:00,224
We need to go.

650
00:51:01,058 --> 00:51:02,977
-How did you even get in here?
-Quiet…

651
00:51:04,979 --> 00:51:06,230
We need to go.

652
00:51:07,648 --> 00:51:09,191
We need to go right now.

653
00:51:13,988 --> 00:51:15,197
So…

654
00:51:16,448 --> 00:51:18,325
You're going to question me at the palace?

655
00:51:26,166 --> 00:51:27,293
Seong Huiju!

656
00:51:35,759 --> 00:51:37,136
Mr. Jung.

657
00:51:38,178 --> 00:51:39,430
Your Royal Highness.

658
00:51:40,806 --> 00:51:43,934
I heard the Royal Ancestral Rite
was being held at Jongmyo Shrine today.

659
00:51:44,518 --> 00:51:46,937
-What brings you by?
-His Majesty is presiding over it.

660
00:51:48,772 --> 00:51:50,524
But what business have you here?

661
00:51:51,900 --> 00:51:54,445
Without authorization
from either His Majesty or me.

662
00:51:57,239 --> 00:51:58,782
I gave the authorization.

663
00:52:08,000 --> 00:52:11,128
As I heard the prime suspect
in the arson case had been identified.

664
00:52:11,754 --> 00:52:12,755
And since she is…

665
00:52:15,007 --> 00:52:17,593
considered a flight risk
and may destroy evidence.

666
00:52:19,595 --> 00:52:21,847
But I did not know that you would be here.

667
00:52:23,307 --> 00:52:24,683
Is there actually any evidence?

668
00:52:25,934 --> 00:52:28,395
As if insulting the Crown
with such insolent attire

669
00:52:29,021 --> 00:52:31,732
and threatening others
within the palace were not enough,

670
00:52:32,483 --> 00:52:33,525
I hear she was absent

671
00:52:34,818 --> 00:52:36,487
at the time of the incident.

672
00:52:37,154 --> 00:52:38,781
Does that constitute evidence?

673
00:52:38,864 --> 00:52:40,074
Perhaps not.

674
00:52:40,157 --> 00:52:42,743
But it should be enough to tarnish…

675
00:52:44,453 --> 00:52:45,871
her reputation

676
00:52:46,455 --> 00:52:48,290
or her company's reputation.

677
00:52:48,999 --> 00:52:50,167
Wait, my company?

678
00:52:53,754 --> 00:52:55,089
Then have me questioned too.

679
00:52:58,634 --> 00:53:01,136
Every circumstance
that casts suspicion on her

680
00:53:02,304 --> 00:53:04,139
applies to me as well.

681
00:53:13,691 --> 00:53:15,359
Will your confidence hold?

682
00:53:17,444 --> 00:53:18,570
I wonder

683
00:53:20,614 --> 00:53:21,865
if yours will hold.

684
00:53:36,338 --> 00:53:38,048
Ms. Seong!

685
00:53:41,885 --> 00:53:43,262
Oh, Your Royal Highness!

686
00:53:43,887 --> 00:53:45,139
-Summon a physician.
-I-AN.

687
00:53:47,015 --> 00:53:49,518
Feel free to come to Anhwadang Hall
for the questioning.

688
00:53:52,271 --> 00:53:54,189
Summon a physician!

689
00:53:54,273 --> 00:53:55,524
Hurry.

690
00:53:57,151 --> 00:53:58,527
Are you all right, Ms. Seong?

691
00:54:23,844 --> 00:54:24,845
Open your eyes.

692
00:54:28,015 --> 00:54:29,808
Wow.

693
00:54:30,768 --> 00:54:31,935
Wow, we totally slayed!

694
00:54:32,019 --> 00:54:33,020
Slayed, my foot.

695
00:54:34,438 --> 00:54:35,898
How could you agree to come here?

696
00:54:37,107 --> 00:54:39,902
That Mr. Jung or whatever
practically dragged me out.

697
00:54:39,985 --> 00:54:40,986
How could I resist?

698
00:54:45,574 --> 00:54:46,575
So…

699
00:54:47,618 --> 00:54:49,244
will I be going to prison?

700
00:54:51,413 --> 00:54:52,414
Does that scare you?

701
00:54:53,916 --> 00:54:55,209
Me?

702
00:54:55,292 --> 00:54:57,336
I'm Seong Huiju of Castle Group.

703
00:54:57,419 --> 00:55:00,005
Prosecutor investigations
and search-and-seizure raids…

704
00:55:00,506 --> 00:55:01,507
Stuff like that

705
00:55:02,090 --> 00:55:04,718
is practically an annual event.

706
00:55:06,178 --> 00:55:10,516
I was just wondering which law firm
I should hire this time.

707
00:55:10,599 --> 00:55:12,726
-Is that something to be proud of?
-I mean,

708
00:55:13,393 --> 00:55:14,895
it's nothing to brag about, but--

709
00:55:14,978 --> 00:55:16,980
She won't be able to act for now.

710
00:55:17,064 --> 00:55:18,899
She knows pursuing you would implicate me,

711
00:55:19,399 --> 00:55:20,901
which would only escalate matters.

712
00:55:25,739 --> 00:55:29,201
But wouldn't you say
that was quite a display?

713
00:55:29,785 --> 00:55:30,911
What was?

714
00:55:30,994 --> 00:55:32,120
Everyone saw it.

715
00:55:32,788 --> 00:55:35,958
The Queen Mother talked about tarnishing
my reputation or whatever.

716
00:55:36,458 --> 00:55:38,126
And you taking my side.

717
00:55:40,963 --> 00:55:42,381
Wake up.

718
00:55:42,464 --> 00:55:44,299
Palace staff do not divulge
palace affairs.

719
00:55:47,427 --> 00:55:48,971
Do you really believe that?

720
00:55:50,639 --> 00:55:53,976
They say the mouth is
the gateway to disaster,

721
00:55:54,059 --> 00:55:56,853
and the tongue is
a blade that cuts the body.

722
00:55:57,354 --> 00:55:59,606
Do you know how many mouths were there?

723
00:56:02,442 --> 00:56:07,239
And you think not a single mouth there
has loose lips?

724
00:56:10,409 --> 00:56:14,496
They probably whipped up
an entire soap opera out of it by now.

725
00:56:17,499 --> 00:56:18,834
I can't believe it.

726
00:56:18,917 --> 00:56:20,836
And still in his ceremonial robe?

727
00:56:21,503 --> 00:56:22,713
I mean, it makes sense.

728
00:56:22,796 --> 00:56:24,756
I heard from an attendant
of the Queen Mother…

729
00:56:24,840 --> 00:56:26,675
I thought it was just a passing scandal,

730
00:56:26,758 --> 00:56:29,595
but as soon as she fainted,
he swept her up in his arms.

731
00:56:29,678 --> 00:56:30,887
It caused quite a stir.

732
00:56:30,971 --> 00:56:32,681
It must be true love!

733
00:56:32,764 --> 00:56:34,016
I know, right?

734
00:56:34,099 --> 00:56:35,350
Hmm.

735
00:56:35,434 --> 00:56:37,144
Plenty of people weren't there.

736
00:56:37,227 --> 00:56:39,187
That doesn't make someone a suspect.

737
00:56:39,271 --> 00:56:41,231
She must've been
so shocked that she fainted.

738
00:56:44,318 --> 00:56:46,653
Your Majesty, are you all right?

739
00:56:46,737 --> 00:56:49,156
Please stay there. I will clean this up.

740
00:56:49,239 --> 00:56:50,324
Court Lady Im.

741
00:56:50,407 --> 00:56:51,617
Is anyone out there?

742
00:56:51,700 --> 00:56:52,909
Court Lady Im!

743
00:56:57,039 --> 00:56:58,832
What are your thoughts?

744
00:56:59,625 --> 00:57:00,667
Pardon?

745
00:57:00,751 --> 00:57:02,002
About what, Your Majesty?

746
00:57:03,378 --> 00:57:05,464
The Grand Prince and that maiden.

747
00:57:05,547 --> 00:57:07,257
Did they seem

748
00:57:08,592 --> 00:57:10,093
genuine in your eyes as well?

749
00:57:20,187 --> 00:57:22,230
-You're not coming with me?
-I have to work.

750
00:57:22,314 --> 00:57:23,523
But it's the weekend.

751
00:57:24,066 --> 00:57:25,067
If I clock out,

752
00:57:26,193 --> 00:57:27,319
someone will kill me.

753
00:57:27,402 --> 00:57:28,737
Who?

754
00:57:30,614 --> 00:57:31,990
Him.

755
00:57:33,200 --> 00:57:35,327
Oh.

756
00:57:36,328 --> 00:57:38,080
Try not to stay up too late, though.

757
00:57:38,664 --> 00:57:39,748
I shall try.

758
00:57:39,831 --> 00:57:41,917
You can call me
if you have trouble sleeping.

759
00:57:42,000 --> 00:57:43,377
I shall.

760
00:57:54,721 --> 00:57:56,306
The more mouths, the better, right?

761
00:58:47,065 --> 00:58:48,066
Your Ladyship!

762
00:58:51,945 --> 00:58:53,530
Are you all right?

763
00:58:53,613 --> 00:58:55,782
What about His Royal Highness?
Is he all right?

764
00:58:57,075 --> 00:58:58,076
Well…

765
00:59:00,203 --> 00:59:02,164
Our dear Steward Kim played a huge role.

766
00:59:02,247 --> 00:59:04,541
I am quite a biker, you see.

767
00:59:04,624 --> 00:59:06,126
Thank you.

768
00:59:07,377 --> 00:59:08,420
Ha!

769
00:59:08,503 --> 00:59:09,588
Applause please.

770
00:59:12,424 --> 00:59:14,092
Well done!

771
00:59:14,176 --> 00:59:15,177
All right!

772
00:59:15,260 --> 00:59:16,303
I'm exhausted.

773
00:59:39,826 --> 00:59:41,036
Still alive?

774
00:59:41,661 --> 00:59:43,580
For now.

775
00:59:45,040 --> 00:59:47,459
I haven't been able to eat,
so I'm starving.

776
00:59:47,542 --> 00:59:50,003
Why not? Is the food not to your liking?

777
00:59:50,086 --> 00:59:51,630
No, I'm just trying to lose weight.

778
00:59:52,130 --> 00:59:53,256
Why?

779
00:59:53,340 --> 00:59:55,342
Looking gaunt will make me
seem more like a victim.

780
00:59:58,178 --> 01:00:00,263
You'll have the Royal Guard
starting tomorrow.

781
01:00:00,889 --> 01:00:01,890
Really?

782
01:00:02,390 --> 01:00:04,309
Is that allowed
when we're not married yet?

783
01:00:04,392 --> 01:00:05,602
It isn't.

784
01:00:05,685 --> 01:00:06,728
I see.

785
01:00:07,229 --> 01:00:09,856
"Another crazy stunt pulled
by the infatuated Grand Prince"?

786
01:00:10,690 --> 01:00:12,567
I guess you can put it like that.

787
01:00:17,113 --> 01:00:18,490
Should I pull one too?

788
01:01:34,149 --> 01:01:36,318
Never thought I'd be doing this.

789
01:01:50,957 --> 01:01:54,794
This is the least we can do
to make them think we're madly in love.

790
01:01:56,212 --> 01:01:57,255
Oh, right.

791
01:02:01,843 --> 01:02:02,844
Here.

792
01:02:04,137 --> 01:02:06,640
This is the tea I drink
when I have trouble sleeping.

793
01:02:07,265 --> 01:02:09,225
It's really expensive, so don't waste it.

794
01:02:10,936 --> 01:02:12,896
One more thing…

795
01:02:15,273 --> 01:02:18,360
This is the magnesium supplement
I take when I really can't asleep.

796
01:02:19,235 --> 01:02:22,864
The side effect is nightmares,
but it's better than not sleeping at all.

797
01:02:25,951 --> 01:02:27,827
-When did I ever ask--
-Stop that.

798
01:02:28,745 --> 01:02:31,164
You didn't see a doctor
after what happened, did you?

799
01:02:35,752 --> 01:02:38,713
Don't you think I'd be
quite the supportive wife?

800
01:02:40,298 --> 01:02:41,383
Hmm.

801
01:03:03,071 --> 01:03:04,155
What are you doing?

802
01:03:12,747 --> 01:03:13,748
Stay still.

803
01:03:53,163 --> 01:03:56,082
PERFECT CROWN

804
01:04:32,160 --> 01:04:33,953
Why would I blush

805
01:04:34,037 --> 01:04:36,873
and get all fluttery over a measly kiss?

806
01:04:36,956 --> 01:04:39,209
You should have maintained decorum.

807
01:04:39,292 --> 01:04:41,795
Then what? Should we make it
a shotgun wedding?

808
01:04:43,004 --> 01:04:45,882
Can I take you somewhere?
Let's speed things up a bit.

809
01:04:46,466 --> 01:04:49,094
The quicker we get married,
the quicker we get divorced.

810
01:04:50,053 --> 01:04:51,054
Smile!

811
01:04:51,137 --> 01:04:53,890
Do you have that much time
to waste?I don't.

812
01:04:54,516 --> 01:04:57,310
That maiden
should move out of your private residence.

813
01:04:57,393 --> 01:05:00,230
Do you have a plan?

814
01:05:01,022 --> 01:05:02,315
Seong Huiju, what's wrong?

815
01:05:02,398 --> 01:05:05,193
Jeongwoo! The brakes aren't working!

816
01:05:11,032 --> 01:05:13,326
Why aren't you answering?

817
01:05:13,993 --> 01:05:16,287
Will you take their side and not mine

818
01:05:16,371 --> 01:05:18,331
because they're your family?

819
01:05:23,253 --> 01:05:24,420
I will take your side.

820
01:05:33,263 --> 01:05:34,347
I must appear

821
01:05:35,306 --> 01:05:36,850
insanely infatuated with you…

822
01:05:45,859 --> 01:05:47,235
…for people to believe

823
01:05:49,154 --> 01:05:50,738
this absurd marriage is genuine.

824
01:06:07,839 --> 01:06:09,841
-What's that?
-It's my hopae.

825
01:06:10,842 --> 01:06:11,843
What about it?

826
01:06:13,261 --> 01:06:15,305
Use it when you need a title behind you

827
01:06:15,388 --> 01:06:16,514
or when you are afraid.

828
01:06:18,850 --> 01:06:21,811
Does it summon a dragon
if I swing it around or something?

829
01:06:29,777 --> 01:06:30,778
It'll summon me.

830
01:06:42,040 --> 01:06:44,042
Translated by Justin S. Kim

831
01:06:55,345 --> 01:06:59,057
PERFECT CROWN
